ActNational Defence Act
PrecisRe-appointment of COLONEL KIM SANDRA CARTER, an officer of the Canadian Forces who is a barrister or advocate of at least ten years standing at the bar of the Province of Ontario, as a military judge, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective January 10, 2006.
